# GSA Startup Kit — Project Context

This is the Green Startup Academy (GSA) Startup Kit. It provides a 23-agent autonomous startup team (12 named team agents + 11 GSA execution agents) and 938+ expert skills for building startups with AI.

## Key Files to Load

- **CLAUDE.md** — Project context, stack defaults, models, rules
- **AGENTS.md** — Agent roster, routing table, slash commands
- Skills live at **`.agent/skills/[skill-name]/SKILL.md`**

## How to Start

Begin any session with: **"Iris, [what I need]"**

Slash commands: `/daily` `/plan` `/ship` `/audit` `/research`

## Skills Usage

Reference skills with `@skill-name` in chat. Example: `@brainstorming help me design a login flow`

Load skills on demand — do not preload. See `.agent/skills/docs/BUNDLES.md` for curated starter packs.
